HEADWORD: Alphol
<hw>Al"phol</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Alpha-</ets> +
<ets>-ol</ets> as in <ets>alcohol</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Pharm.)</fld>
